column2: SELECT s.specObjID, s.ra, s.dec, s.z, s.zErr, s.class, s.zWarning, s.snMedian, zp.modelMag_u as u, zp.modelMag_g as g, zp.modelMag_r as r, zp.modelMag_i as i, zp.modelMag_z as z, u-g, g-r, r-i, i-z FROM SpecObjAll as s  JOIN dbo.fGetNearbyObjEq(#, #, #) AS GN ON s.bestObjID = GN.objID  JOIN PhotoObjAll as zp ON zp.objID = s.bestObjID  WHERE  s.class = &&& AND   s.zWarning=# ORDER BY distance
